</taxonomicName>
requires the new combination below. Since 
<taxonomicName id="4C194D2DFFB8A22ADE5EFBE4D6E31A7E" authorityName="Salvator NTORE &amp; Olivier LACHENAUD" authorityYear="2019" baseAuthorityName="K. Schum." box="[529,675,1113,1139]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rubiaceae" genus="Pauridiantha" kingdom="Plantae" order="Gentianales" pageId="5" pageNumber="32" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="chlorantha">
<emphasis id="B96DEABCFFB8A22ADE5EFBE4D6E31A7E" box="[529,675,1113,1139]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="32">R. chlorantha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is rather little-known and its previous descriptions (
<bibRefCitation id="EF884B5FFFB8A22ADE02FBC7D6BF1A9E" author="SCHUMANN K." box="[589,767,1145,1171]" journalOrPublisher="Botanische Jahrbucher fur Systematik, Pflanzengeschichte und Pflanzengeographie" pageId="5" pageNumber="32" pagination="55 - 113" part="28" publicationUrl="https://biodiversitylibrary.org/page/210526" refId="ref9356" refString="SCHUMANN K. 1899. - Rubiaceae Africanae. Botanische Jahrbucher fur Systematik, Pflanzengeschichte und Pflanzengeographie 28: 55 - 113. https: // biodiversitylibrary. org / page / 210526" title="Rubiaceae Africanae" type="journal article" year="1899">Schumann 1899</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EF884B5FFFB8A22ADCCBFB27D5041ABE" author="BREMEKAMP C. E. B." box="[132,324,1177,1203]" journalOrPublisher="Botanische Jahrbucher fur Systematik, Pflanzengeschichte und Pflanzengeographie" pageId="5" pageNumber="32" pagination="200 - 227" part="71" refId="ref8668" refString="BREMEKAMP C. E. B. 1940. - Ist die Gattung Urophyllum Wall. in Afrika vertreten? Botanische Jahrbucher fur Systematik, Pflanzengeschichte und Pflanzengeographie 71: 200 - 227." title="Ist die Gattung Urophyllum Wall. in Afrika vertreten?" type="journal article" year="1940">Bremekamp 1940</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EF884B5FFFB8A22ADD1FFB27D5B91ABE" author="VERDCOURT B." bookContentInfo="414 p." box="[336,505,1177,1203]" editor="POLHILL R. M." journalOrPublisher="Crown Agents for Overseas Governments &amp; Administrations, London" pageId="5" pageNumber="32" refId="ref9498" refString="VERDCOURT B. 1976. - Rubiaceae (part 1), in POLHILL R. M. (ed.), Flora of Tropical East Africa. Crown Agents for Overseas Governments &amp; Administrations, London, 414 p." title="Rubiaceae (part 1)" type="book" volumeTitle="Flora of Tropical East Africa" year="1976">Verdcourt 1976</bibRefCitation>
) were incomplete on several points, a complete and updated account of this species is presented here.
</paragraph>
